  "instructions": [
    "Preheat grill to medium-high heat.",
    "Cut tofu into 1-inch cubes.",
    "In a shallow dish, whisk together soy sauce, rice vinegar, ginger, garlic, red pepper flakes, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add tofu cubes to the marinade and toss to coat. Let it marinate for at least 30 minutes, or up to 2 hours in the refrigerator.",
    "Thread tofu cubes onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece.",
